Text: Fuck yeah, dude. For the power of friendship.
GENIUS. After "The Art of the Dress," I had no choice but to go looking for a download. Thanks for being there!

Thanks for the songs! I was looking for Winter
wrap up in mp3 since I first saw that episode,
and Rarity singing Art of the dress is a nice 
bonus. I put it on my mp3 player at work (don't
tell my boss) and listened to it all the way home 
on the bus today. BROHOOF!
